                "showMiniMap": false
              },
              "content": "#### Targets status\n\nEach line in this panel shows the number and percentage of targets being up for each job. When the percentage is below **100%** it means there is a problem while trying to monitor one or more targets. The related errors can be found in [Alloy UI](https://grafana.com/docs/alloy/latest/troubleshoot/debug/).\n",
              "mode": "markdown"
            }
          },
          "version": "13.1.0-local"
